						Position   Button Name
						0         1
						1         2
						2         A
						3         B (toggle button on back of device)
						4         Plus
						5         Minus
						6         Rocker Left
						7         Rocker Right
						8         Rocker Up
						9         Rocker Down
						10        HOME
